{"tid":2039991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「行動」有新方法，去表達對國安法不滿","createTime":"2020-05-28T09:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T10:44:39.000Z","uid":341589,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b434d33067a60d9ec5b61a05c99494f67054f3b6","tid":2039991,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:58:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">國安法係人大剛剛通過，並<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不代表香港人已經輸左，可以放棄抗爭</span></span>。而家我地要盡快在港共政權再有下一步行動前，盡快重聚當初反送中時嘅人氣同民意，向世界表達香港人對國安法基定嘅反對，同對中國共產黨及港共政權的不滿。因只靠香港人相信好難反抗，要令世界各國因立法<span style=\"font-size: large;\">而起港共及時施壓。當米已成炊時，已後悔莫及。<br />\n<br />\n早幾日，同屋企深藍長輩再一次「交流」，佢地提醒左一個有用嘅抗爭方法。80及90後，應該記得2005年韓國農民來港用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「三步一拜」</span></span>方法抗議世貿會議。結果在極短時間，令香港人產生關注及同情。而家香港情勢危急，若果只繼續利用和你唱，和你lunch或火魔等方法，對家只會依舊用一如既往方法，去誣蔑手足破壞社會秩序，更加反證立法需要。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地要集思廣益，諗多D新嘅抗爭方法。</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n以下係當年有關韓農「三步一拜」報導供參考，05:50開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9ocg1gpqocY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9ocg1gpqocY&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=0b2da8cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9ocg1gpqocY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0MM9WbA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0MM9WbA.png&h=48d53c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力，要珍惜最後可以反抗嘅機會</span></span></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a91688d64df2063710d982e962e5912a268ecd9","tid":2039991,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep